<leg xml:space="preserve" billnum="SB0045" sponsor="Michael K. McKell" designation="SB" otherSponsor="" otherHouse="House" subNumber="01" subSponsor="Todd Weiler" sess="2026GS" fileno="2026FL1099" date="2/4/2026 11:02:633" printDate="02-04 11:45" subVer="1" minVer="0" office="LEGISLATIVE GENERAL COUNSEL" actionDate="" impact="code"><info><nextbuid>7</nextbuid><aminfo anum="0" effdate="05/06/2026"><seclist><sect action="A" src="code" buid="2" uid="C4-45-S105_2026050620260506" fromuid="C4-45-S105_2019051420190514" sort="04 45 01050020260506" mtype="section" effdate="05/06/2026">4-45-105</sect><sect action="E" src="code" buid="5" uid="C58-38a-S205_2026050620260506" sort="58 38a02050020260506" mtype="section" effdate="05/06/2026">58-38a-205</sect><sect src="uncod" untype="effdate" buid="6" uid="EF0000" sort="UZEFF" mtype="uncod" effdate="05/06/2026"/></seclist></aminfo></info><tbox><sinfo><nextpairid>0</nextpairid></sinfo><st numlevel="1" lineno="1" slineno="0-1">Kratom Adjustments</st><sessionhead>2026 GENERAL SESSION</sessionhead><statehead>STATE OF UTAH</statehead><sponsorhead>Chief Sponsor: Michael K. McKell</sponsorhead><otherSponsorhead>House Sponsor: </otherSponsorhead></tbox><lt numlevel="1" lineno="2" slineno="0-2"><lthead lineno="3">LONG TITLE</lthead><gdhead lineno="4">General Description:</gdhead><gd numlevel="1" lineno="5" slineno="0-5">This bill amends provisions related to kratom.</gd><hphead lineno="6">Highlighted Provisions:</hphead><hp numlevel="1" lineno="7" slineno="0-7">This bill:<hl numlevel="1" lineno="8" slineno="0-8" level="1">prohibits the sale of kratom to an individual under 21 years old; and</hl><hl numlevel="1" lineno="9" slineno="0-9" level="1">requires the Controlled Substance Advisory Committee to issue a report on kratom <ln numlevel="1" lineno="10" slineno="0-10"/>products that are able to be sold in the state.</hl></hp><moni numlevel="1" lineno="11" slineno="0-11" display="none">Money Appropriated in this Bill:</moni><moniNone lineno="12">None</moniNone><oc numlevel="1" lineno="13" slineno="0-13">Other Special Clauses:</oc><ocNone lineno="14">None</ocNone><sa numlevel="1" lineno="15" slineno="0-15">Utah Code Sections Affected:<saamd numlevel="1" lineno="16" slineno="0-16"><snhead>AMENDS:</snhead><sn num="4-45-105" src="code" uid="C4-45-S105_2026050620260506" buid="2" sort="04 45 01050020260506" numlevel="1" lineno="17" slineno="0-17"><bold>4-45-105</bold>, as enacted by Laws of Utah 2019, Chapter 329</sn></saamd><saent numlevel="1" lineno="18" slineno="0-18"><snhead>ENACTS:</snhead><sn num="58-38a-205" src="code" uid="C58-38a-S205_2026050620260506" buid="5" sort="58 38a02050020260506" numlevel="1" lineno="19" slineno="0-19"><bold>58-38a-205</bold>, Utah Code Annotated 1953</sn></saent></sa></lt><enacthead lineno="20"/><enact numlevel="1" lineno="21" slineno="0-21">Be it enacted by the Legislature of the state of Utah:</enact><bdy><bsec buid="2" num="4-45-105" type="amend" src="code" uid="C4-45-S105_2026050620260506" sort="04 45 01050020260506" numlevel="1" lineno="22" slineno="1-1" sn="1"><section number="4-45-105" numlevel="1" lineno="23" slineno="1-2" type="amend"><secline lineno="22">Section 1. Section <bold>4-45-105</bold> is amended to read:</secline><catline lineno="23"><bold>4-45-105<parens/>. Prohibition on sale to minors -- Criminal penalty.</bold></catline><subsection ssid="2-null-1" dnum="1-o" numlevel="1" lineno="24" slineno="1-3" level="1" placement="noreturn"><display>(1)</display>A kratom processor may not distribute, sell, or offer for sale a kratom product to an <ln numlevel="1" lineno="25" slineno="1-4"/>individual under <amendoutstart style="2"/><amend anum="0" ea="erase" pairid="3" groupid="3" style="2" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" deltag="both">18</amend><amendoutend style="2"/><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="2" groupid="2" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="both" space="true">21</amend> years of age.</subsection><subsection ssid="2-null-2" dnum="2-o" numlevel="1" lineno="26" slineno="1-5" level="1"><display>(2)</display>A kratom processor who violates this section is guilty of a class C misdemeanor for <ln numlevel="1" lineno="27" slineno="1-6"/>each violation.</subsection></section></bsec><bsec buid="5" num="58-38a-205" type="enact" src="code" uid="C58-38a-S205_2026050620260506" sort="58 38a02050020260506" numlevel="1" lineno="28" slineno="2-1" sn="2"><section numlevel="1" lineno="29" slineno="2-2" number="58-38a-205" type="enact"><secline lineno="28">Section 2. Section <bold>58-38a-205</bold> is enacted to read:</secline><catline lineno="29"><bold>58-38a-205<parens/>. Kratom study.</bold></catline><subsection ssid="5-2" dnum="_-o:1-i" numlevel="1" lineno="30" slineno="2-3" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="1" placement="noreturn"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1002" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(1)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="23" groupid="17" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">As used in this section, "kratom product" means the same as that term is defined in <ln numlevel="1" lineno="31" slineno="2-4"/>Section <xref depth="3" refnumber="4-45-102">4-45-102</xref>.</amend></subsection><subsection ssid="5-3" dnum="_-o:2-i" numlevel="1" lineno="32" slineno="2-5" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="1"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1003" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(2)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="15" groupid="10" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">The committee shall:</amend><subsection ssid="5-5" dnum="_-o:a-i" numlevel="1" lineno="33" slineno="2-6" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="2"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1004" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(a)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="29" groupid="21" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">review scientific, medical, and regulatory information related to kratom products that <ln numlevel="1" lineno="34" slineno="2-7"/>comply with Section <xref depth="3" refnumber="4-45-104">4-45-104</xref>;</amend></subsection><subsection ssid="5-1" dnum="_-o:b-i" numlevel="1" lineno="35" slineno="2-8" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="2"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1005" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(b)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="3" groupid="3" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">evaluate the safety profile, patterns of use, and appropriate regulatory framework for <ln numlevel="1" lineno="36" slineno="2-9"/>kratom products described in Subsection <xref depth="4" refnumber="58-38a-205(2)(a)">(2)(a)</xref>; and</amend></subsection><subsection ssid="5-6" dnum="_-o:c-i" numlevel="1" lineno="37" slineno="2-10" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="2"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1006" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(c)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="35" groupid="26" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">submit a written report, including recommendations for legislative action, to the <ln numlevel="1" lineno="38" slineno="2-11"/>Health and Human Services Interim Committee no later than January 15, 2027.</amend></subsection></subsection></section></bsec><bsec buid="6" type="uncod" untype="effdate" src="uncod" uid="EF0000" sort="UZEFF" langlock="true" numlevel="1" lineno="39" slineno="3-1" sn="3"><section type="uncod" untype="effdate" display="false" src="uncod"><secline lineno="39">Section 3.  <bold>Effective Date.</bold></secline><sectionText lineno="40"><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1" groupid="1" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="both">This bill takes effect on <effdate uid="code" date="5/6/2026">May 6, 2026</effdate>.</amend></sectionText></section></bsec></bdy><foot><rev><tm>2-4-26 11:45 AM</tm></rev></foot></leg>